00:19:15,330 --> 00:19:18,290
Would it be possible for me
to attend the trial?

258
00:19:19,250 --> 00:19:23,050
You're not required to appear,
but you can if you'd like.

259
00:19:23,130 --> 00:19:25,510
Then, I'll see you at the trial.

260
00:19:25,590 --> 00:19:27,390
Please don't tell Mr. Kim.

261
00:19:29,430 --> 00:19:30,510
All right, then.

262
00:19:35,100 --> 00:19:38,230
I'm telling you,
I have no way of finding that out.

263
00:19:38,310 --> 00:19:39,940
You can just sit in on the trial.

264
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:42,900
I'll let you know
the courtroom number and time.

265
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:46,950
