-As it should be.

276
00:20:09,850 --> 00:20:11,260
They put food on our table.

277
00:20:11,930 --> 00:20:13,930
Everything you've enjoyed came from them.

278
00:20:14,020 --> 00:20:15,890
Not anymore. Count me out.

279
00:20:16,980 --> 00:20:19,940
Wanting out won't make it happen.
We're a family business.

280
00:20:20,020 --> 00:20:21,440
Family business, my foot.

281
00:20:22,070 --> 00:20:23,070
Goodness.

282
00:20:35,540 --> 00:20:37,120
Get your rice cakes!

283
00:20:37,210 --> 00:20:38,250
For crying out loud.

284
00:20:38,330 --> 00:20:40,830
-You going around selling rice cakes now?
-You little…

285
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:43,090
Who still uses
bojagi wrapping cloth like this?

286
00:20:43,170 --> 00:20:44,590
I'm busy. Move.

287
00:20:45,630 --> 00:20:46,630
Later.

288
00:21:05,070 --> 00:21:06,650
You look young.

289
00:21:08,150 --> 00:21:09,280
Thank you.

290
00:21:09,910 --> 00:21:11,490
Are you really a lawyer?

291
00:21:11,570 --> 00:21:12,740
-Yes.
-How many years in?

292
00:21:13,330 --> 00:21:14,330
Me?

293
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:18,330
About seven or eight years.

294
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,830
Really? So you're not a newbie.

295
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:23,210
A law school graduate?

296
00:21:23,960 --> 00:21:25,630
-Yes.
-You must come from money.

297
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:27,300
Sorry?

298
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:30,380
Nothing. Please keep reading.

299
00:21:42,730 --> 00:21:44,230
Yes, hello?

300
00:21:44,310 --> 00:21:46,480
Hello, I'm Attorney Kang Huiji.

301
00:21:46,570 --> 00:21:48,780
I'm reaching out
through Ms. Kang Jeongyun.

302
00:21:49,950 --> 00:21:52,360
Yes, I heard. Hello.

303
00:21:52,450 --> 00:21:54,830
Hello. Whenever we have a medical lawsuit,

304
00:21:54,910 --> 00:21:56,540
