305
00:21:56,620 --> 00:21:58,290
Thank you, as always.

306
00:21:58,370 --> 00:22:01,160
Did you get a chance
to review the footage we sent?

307
00:22:01,250 --> 00:22:02,580
Yes, I did.

308
00:22:02,670 --> 00:22:05,210
But there was nothing strange about it.

309
00:22:05,290 --> 00:22:09,460
His hands seem a little slow,
but some doctors just work slowly.

310
00:22:10,050 --> 00:22:13,970
-Then, what caused the shock?
-It's usually unpredictable.

311
00:22:14,050 --> 00:22:15,760
And there are thousands of causes.

312
00:22:16,300 --> 00:22:19,520
Sudden deaths like this
are beyond what humans can control.

313
00:22:22,060 --> 00:22:25,190
I see. Thank you for your time, Doctor.

314
00:22:26,820 --> 00:22:27,820
Goodbye.

315
00:22:49,630 --> 00:22:51,880
We'll proceed with the next case.

316
00:22:51,970 --> 00:22:56,930
Civil case number 2024-24215,
please step forward.

317
00:22:58,010 --> 00:23:01,520
Plaintiff, Min Subin.
Defendant, Gonggang Industries.

318
00:23:05,150 --> 00:23:06,650
I didn't say you could sit.

319
00:23:09,070 --> 00:23:10,110
I apologize.

320
00:23:16,910 --> 00:23:18,030
Please be seated.

321
00:23:20,330 --> 00:23:24,040
