and perforation,

347
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:46,410
so they usually remove them
with laparoscopy.

348
00:24:46,500 --> 00:24:48,370
But inflammation means open surgery.

349
00:24:48,460 --> 00:24:50,420
Wait, how do you even know that?

350
00:24:53,460 --> 00:24:56,050
What? You said to help
if you didn't know something.

351
00:24:56,130 --> 00:24:58,220
But I knew very well this time.

352
00:24:58,300 --> 00:24:59,590
Don't empathize.

353
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:01,340
It's just work.

354
00:25:01,430 --> 00:25:04,430
If you empathize, you'll lose objectivity
and hinder your work.

355
00:25:05,020 --> 00:25:08,230
Juhyeong, stop pretending like
you're choosing not to empathize.

356
00:25:08,310 --> 00:25:10,730
You don't empathize,
because you can't feel anything.

357
00:25:10,810 --> 00:25:12,190
It's not by choice, okay?

358
00:25:13,860 --> 00:25:16,150
You two are bantering a lot more now.

359
00:25:16,230 --> 00:25:17,780
I thought we'd gotten closer.

360
00:25:17,860 --> 00:25:19,610
Yeah, I am closer with you.

361
00:25:19,700 --> 00:25:20,910
-Right?
-Yeah.

362
00:25:23,780 --> 00:25:24,950
Did you just wink?

363
00:25:25,040 --> 00:25:27,250
-Want one too?
-This day's been so brutal.

364
00:25:32,830 --> 00:25:33,840
Goddamn it.

365
00:25:33,920 --> 00:25:35,590
-Wet wipes.
-Wet wipes.

366
00:25:37,010 --> 00:25:38,010
Hey, use this first.

367
00:25:38,090 --> 00:25:39,090
-In the back.
-Hey.

368
00:26:03,450 --> 00:26:04,700
Yes?

369
00:26:07,120 --> 00:26:09,910
Ma'am, I just got back
from the verdict for Kang Yungu's case.

370
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:12,080
We won 650 million won.

371
00:26:12,830 --> 00:26:15,590
-Really? That's a relief.
-Yes.

372
00:26:15,670 --> 00:26:17,920
I'll let you know
once the judgment's delivered.

373
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:19,380
-Okay, thank you.
-Sure.

374
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:26,050
At least that's good news.

375
00:26:31,180 --> 00:26:32,310
KANG YUNGU

376
00:26:34,690 --> 00:26:36,190
-Hello?
-Did you hear the verdict?

377
00:26:36,270 --> 00:26:39,980
-Yes, I did. Thankfully--
-Why is it only 650 million won?

378
00:26:40,070 --> 00:26:42,820
I filed for 700 million won.
Where's the rest?

379
00:26:42,900 --> 00:26:47,410
About that.
The 50 million was confirmed as repaid.

380
00:26:47,490 --> 00:26:49,950
We planned to reduce
that part of the claim anyway--

381
00:26:50,040 --> 00:26:51,620
I said I didn't get that money.

382
00:26:52,960 --> 00:26:55,580
You received the 50 million
and it's all on record.

383
00:26:55,670 --> 00:26:58,130
What are you going to do
about the 50 million won?

384
00:27:00,800 --> 00:27:04,340
Mr. Kang,
out of the 700 million we claimed,

385
00:27:04,430 --> 00:27:08,640
about 400 million
had no direct evidence of--

386
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:12,390
