why did we only win 650 million?

387
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:14,940
Why did you lose 50 million won? Why?

388
00:27:24,530 --> 00:27:26,660
-Attorney Ahn.
-Yes, what is it?

389
00:27:29,910 --> 00:27:30,990
What? Are you hungry?

390
00:27:32,500 --> 00:27:33,790
No, it's not that.

391
00:27:41,210 --> 00:27:43,300
-Here.
-I said it's not that.

392
00:28:03,030 --> 00:28:04,240
Want to grab drinks later?

393
00:28:04,320 --> 00:28:06,280
Are you an alcoholic? Give it a rest.

394
00:28:07,240 --> 00:28:08,240
Okay.

395
00:28:13,750 --> 00:28:15,200
Thank you for the snack.

396
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:20,460
When do you want to grab dinner?

397
00:28:20,540 --> 00:28:21,920
I have dinner plans.

398
00:28:23,500 --> 00:28:24,550
Everyone's busy.

399
00:28:26,130 --> 00:28:27,220
Got it. Bye.

400
00:28:47,240 --> 00:28:49,780
Something feels off.

401
00:28:51,280 --> 00:28:52,580
What could it be?

402
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:58,040
MEDICAL RECORD

403
00:29:04,550 --> 00:29:05,760
PERFORATION

404
00:29:18,520 --> 00:29:21,190
Attorney Bae, did we lose Mr. Kang's case?

405
00:29:21,270 --> 00:29:22,810
Sorry? Lose his case?

406
00:29:22,900 --> 00:29:25,020
Yes, Mr. Kang is in an uproar right now.

407
00:29:26,530 --> 00:29:29,950
Sir, we won 650 million
out of 700 million.

408
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:32,160
Then, why is he going nuts
and saying we lost?

409
00:29:32,820 --> 00:29:33,990
I have no idea either.

410
00:29:34,080 --> 00:29:36,790
It was confirmed the 50 million
was already repaid,

411
00:29:36,870 --> 00:29:40,370
-so we suggested reducing the claim--
-Got it. Let's talk again tomorrow.

412
00:29:52,300 --> 00:29:54,010
ATTORNEY BAE MUNJEONG

413
00:29:55,010 --> 00:29:58,470
ATTORNEY HA SANGGI

414
00:30:01,480 --> 00:30:03,900
