-No.

417
00:30:09,440 --> 00:30:11,950
-No, look at this clause right here.
-Here?

418
00:30:12,030 --> 00:30:13,490
-This one?
-No, here.

419
00:30:14,530 --> 00:30:16,120
I didn't see this before.

420
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:17,240
Cheers.

421
00:30:21,210 --> 00:30:23,370
