423
00:30:25,380 --> 00:30:27,130
-What?
-I'm a K-pop idol.

424
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:30,260
-Come on.
-It's the truth.

425
00:30:30,340 --> 00:30:32,430
I wasn't a famous K-pop idol.

426
00:30:32,510 --> 00:30:33,550
But I really was one.

427
00:30:33,630 --> 00:30:36,430
And one day, I thought about
giving studying a shot and--

428
00:30:36,510 --> 00:30:38,770
MUNJEONG

429
00:30:49,900 --> 00:30:51,030
Bastards.

430
00:30:52,280 --> 00:30:54,490
They're never around
when you actually need them.

431
00:31:21,060 --> 00:31:23,390
Let's finish this up tomorrow.

432
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:25,770
-Yes, ma'am.
-Okay.

433
00:31:26,980 --> 00:31:29,610
