435
00:31:36,660 --> 00:31:37,660
Of course.

436
00:31:37,740 --> 00:31:40,410
-In that case, sounds good.
-Okay.

437
00:31:40,990 --> 00:31:43,080
I'll go wrap up then, ma'am.

438
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:44,330
-Okay.
-All right.

439
00:31:47,540 --> 00:31:50,380
