440
00:32:01,310 --> 00:32:02,310
Okay.

441
00:32:03,220 --> 00:32:04,930
She didn't even open the door for me.

442
00:32:13,070 --> 00:32:14,070
Gosh.

443
00:32:18,870 --> 00:32:20,700
ATTORNEY BAE MUNJEONG

444
00:32:22,660 --> 00:32:24,450
ATTORNEY BAE MUNJEONG

445
00:32:24,540 --> 00:32:26,210
