00:32:46,480 --> 00:32:49,810
ATTORNEY AHN JUHYEONG

450
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:56,360
ATTORNEY BAE MUNJEONG

451
00:33:56,460 --> 00:33:57,550
Let's go now.

