464
00:34:50,930 --> 00:34:51,930
Hyungmin Building.

465
00:34:53,270 --> 00:34:54,480
Kim Hyungmin.

466
00:34:56,860 --> 00:34:58,190
-I see!
-Yes.

467
00:35:01,190 --> 00:35:03,240
Okay, get home safe.

468
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:04,320
Thank you.

469
00:35:04,910 --> 00:35:07,240
Feel free to swing by my office next time.

470
00:35:07,990 --> 00:35:09,040
Yes, I will.

471
00:35:09,120 --> 00:35:10,620
-Okay.
